Procedure.history:
Version 4.0 (AdF - 09.03.2023)
Change History:
- Copied from FOM procedure N_SAT_I600 Version 9 - 15/04/2022
- Procedure Description field updated according to EUMETSAT template;
- GeoSAR management removed, as per PST recommendation provided via email by ESA (Emilia Barbagallo), on Tuesday 7 March 2023 11:12, Subject: RE: Yaw Flip Manoeuvre preparation;
- introduced IF steps to execute PL management only if needed: no action if PL is in Wait or lower macro-mode;
- introduced variables to record the PL status at the start of the procedure, in order to restore it after the Yaw Flip manoeuvre execution;
- introduced Operator interactions to provide the oprion to skip FCI or LI calibrations;
- FCI to Wait procedure: call to N_SAT_I510 replaced by call to N_FCI_I205;
- Steps executing PF and PDD activities replaced by a call to EUM version of N_SAT_I600, that was updated to manage only PF and KAT gain setting Ka antenna re-pointing; 
- FCI to Observation procedure: call to N_SAT_I500 replaced by call to N_FCI_I800;
- Added procedure arguments to populate N_FCI_I800 from parent procedure N_SAT_I800;
- Fixed typos in procedure arguments related to N_FCI_I800.
